Package: mlbstatsR
Type: Package
Title: Stats, Photos, Logos, and Colors of M.L.B. Baseball
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ivan Villanueva
Maintainer: Ivan Villanueva <ivan.v23@yahoo.com>
Description: M.L.B. data with stats photos logos and colors.
    Package of stats, photos, logos and the colors of the M.L.B. teams.
    This package gives users the ability to work with M.L.B. data in a clean and detailed way.
    Which provides users with a variety of ways to improve visualizations.
